<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Bethelehem Dak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngai un Bethlehem dak agii,
 Van mi a hung kikhawm;
 Van Lal Immanuel chawian di'n,
 Belam chingte a hung ui,
 Aw, ei hawn le chawian hitiu.

[V2]
 A gi a hawih na e!
 Kristmas' dakin ka lung a kuoi;
 Bethlehem ei hetsak hi,
 Michingte guola chieh dingin;
 Ka thagau, nang le kisa'n.

[V3]
 2. Michingte mapui van Aksi,
 Bethlehem ei tunin;
 Van lal kuolna bawng In tawmah,
 Sunsawt chawmsak ka nuom hi,
 Mi ngaihin munniem himahleh.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa Kristmas vang hun pie'n la,
 A lawpte lunggilah;
 Gam tuolthing pak lunlai guolin,
 Van Lal lopina dingin,
 Van kipahna chu paksak in.</lyrics>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>27</hymn_number>
</song>